{"tid":1033184,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2019DSE自修] 3/3/2019 中文聽綜、閱讀Mock Exam","createTime":"2019-02-23T02:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T06:38:46.000Z","uid":125535,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72d7b9ff790f46e8dd5f191a3128dd886e73fab3","tid":1033184,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:49:49.000Z","msg":"三月三日星期日有一場中文Mock, 考聽綜同埋閱讀卷, 由社福機構舉辦, 免費既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當日有老師即場改聽綜卷同埋解卷, 有冇自修既同學想參加?<br />\n<br />\n日期: 3/3/2019 (星期日)<br />\n時間: 1:30PM至8:00PM<br />\n地點: 麗瑤邨既社區中心 (美孚站/荔景站轉乘小巴)<br />\n試卷: 聽綜卷 及 閱讀卷<br />\n對象: 自修生<br />\n費用: 免費<span style=\"color: purple;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n當日流程<br />\n1:30-4:00 聽綜卷 (2.5小時)<br />\n4:00-4:15 小休<br />\n4:15-5:45 閱讀卷 (1.5小時)<br />\n5:45-6:15 中休<br />\n6:15-8:00 派發及講解試卷<br />\n8:00-9:00 一齊食野嗎?<br />\n<br />\n*老師會即場批改聽綜卷，解卷時將發回給大家<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既同學可以係Google Form留低聯絡方法，會盡快聯絡你。最後一個月，各位加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Form: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/McBGUavCPeN0vMRG2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FMcBGUavCPeN0vMRG2&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1Ltp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=5f8f4d4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/McBGUavCPeN0vMRG2</a>"},{"pid":"0300a53f5daf465e0d45358fd2444656c133d705","tid":1033184,"uid":42374,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"係咪個個都入得麗瑤？"},{"pid":"2d9528e80b5c8e986eec00ee4e910cffcdb5a75f","tid":1033184,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"輕推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5059a2d19562e573b98f775b364135a8f7cb66","tid":1033184,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:57:01.000Z","msg":"輕輕推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj